Folder Structure

üì• 2. File Input Extraction Pipeline
Screenshots / Images
Apply OCR using Tesseract or PaddleOCR
Clean text (remove noise)
PDFs
PyMuPDF for fast extraction
On error ‚Üí fallback to OCR
Links
Fetch metadata (title, description, favicon)
Text Inputs
Used as-is
All end up in this format:
{"type": "email" | "pdf" | "image" | "link" | "text","raw_content": "...","extracted_text": "...","metadata": {...}}
üß† 3. Categorization Engine (LLM call)
Runs one structured prompt:
TASK: Classify the content into one of:
Event
Task
Bill / Payment
Reminder
Document
Link
And extract structured fields: 
For example for a bill:
{"category": "bill","title": "Water Bill","amount": 18.72,"due_date": "2025-11-21","confidence": 0.92}
For an event:
{"category": "event","title": "Dinner with Emma","datetime": "2025-11-18 19:00","location": "Downtown Cafe"}
