üì¨ 3. Gmail Ingestion Flow (Google ADK)
Agent Calls: 
gmail.search("newer_than:7d")
gmail.get_message(id)
Extract: sender, subject, datetime, body text, attachments (PDF/JPG/PNG). Attachments are auto-sent through the extraction pipeline
